Date:   Sun Dec 29 14:17:10 2013 +0100

    fx2lafw: Fix incorrect unitsize when a trigger fires.
    
    The unitsize was always being set to 2, regardless of whether an fx2lafw
    device with 8 or 16 probes was used.
    
    This fixes bug #182.

