commit ca070ed9a0237e5cea10e5dd974e06da62de890d
Author: Uwe Hermann <uwe@hermann-uwe.de>
Date:   Thu Feb 2 21:15:04 2012 +0100

    sr: Make more symbols private via static/SR_PRIV.
    
